{"tid":2337114,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得木耳單嘢會搞到木耳唔再相信人","createTime":"2020-12-23T05:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T06:08:08.000Z","uid":87428,"like":16,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ff20b58c371133fcf429e9bca02db067f2f1c0e7","tid":2337114,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:35:49.000Z","msg":"變吉良吉影<br />\n<br />\n我的名字叫吉良吉影，33歲。住在杜王町東北部的別墅區一帶，未婚。我在龜友連鎖店服務。每天都要加班到晚上8點才能回家。我不抽煙，酒僅止於淺嚐。晚上11點睡，每天要睡足8個小時。睡前，我一定喝一杯溫牛奶，然後做20分鐘的柔軟操，上了床，馬上熟睡。一覺到天亮，決不把疲勞和壓力留到第二天。醫生都說我很正常。"},{"pid":"cb3493db513b3cda0dabfae384f51893adb4e113","tid":2337114,"uid":225595,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:41:55.000Z","msg":"波嫂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cfb877d188db8649b5ecafedfaa63feb2ae664","tid":2337114,"uid":342823,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:44:32.000Z","msg":"佢咁好樣,使咩驚."},{"pid":"60d8c960a596244fe5d2fca3c1f073920193176c","tid":2337114,"uid":24596,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}